      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i'm \"supposed\" to feel like i matter, but honestly it just feels like a script. like, my manager only pings me for updates, and my friends only text when they need something. if i just didn't log on tomorrow, it wouldn't be a tragedy, it'd just be a minor inconvenience in a ticket queue. there's no weight to me. i feel like a ghost that's just haunting an office chair.",
